<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٠٢١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5889">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ كَثِيرٍ </a>: أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6437">مُوسَى بْنِ عُقْبَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«حَرَّقَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> نَخْلَ بَنِي النَّضِيرِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>